// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0659 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: b9dfc4a6-304f-5d43-b706-bd07708c5351

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:2022*" or process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:2023*" or process.executable like~ "*azure linux:3.0*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:22.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:22.10*")
